column2: SELECT TOP #  photoobj.run, photoobj.camcol, photoobj.field, photoobj.obj,  photoobj.psfmag_u, photoobj.psfmag_g, photoobj.psfmag_r,  photoobj.psfmag_i, photoobj.psfmag_z,   photoobj.ra as photoobj_ra, photoobj.dec as photoobj_dec,   star.apstar_id, star.ra as star_ra, star.dec as star_dec,   aspcap.teff, aspcap.param_m_h, aspcap.logg FROM apogeeStar AS star   CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( star.ra, star.dec, #) AS near   JOIN photoobj ON near.objid=photoobj.objid   JOIN aspcapStar as aspcap ON star.apstar_id = aspcap.apstar_id WHERE star.glat > #. and aspcap.teff > #
